messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

Hello, my name's Ann. Thank you for your published prayer. I am fighting with the spirit of lust and I have found your site. During my reading your prayer, I feel the love of God and I feel the power of this prayer. If possible, I would like to translate the prayer into my language and post it for other people in my country can pray this and be delivered from the spirit of lust.
